                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1717" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0100</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9177 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪的创新成功之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The innovation success of BYD</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王成军，叶伟巍等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新管理；企业战略；企业文化；资源优化配置；技术创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Innovation Management, Corporate Strategy, Corporate Culture Resource Optimization , Technology Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪汽车始终坚持自主品牌、自主研发、自主发展的发展模式，以“打造民族的世界级汽车品牌”为产业目标，在步入汽车行业短短的十年内就成为世界汽车行业的新宠。2008年，比亚迪得到“股神”巴菲特的青睐；自2010 年起比亚迪开始大规模运营新能源汽车，至今已在25个国家得到推广；2014年王传福获得“扎耶德未来能源奖”终身成就奖，比亚迪的三大绿色梦想与城市公交电动化再度获得国际认可。本案例围绕比亚迪公司有关汽车产品的开发战略、特色的企业文化和公司资源优化配置三个模块的“相辅相成”来研究它的创新成功之道，旨在对企业在发展中制定并调整其创新战略和开发有效的商业模式提供借鉴指导。本案例适用于MBA教学的《技术创新管理》、《服务创新》等课程，尤其是在技术创新等方面的案例教学讨论中使用。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">BYD Auto has always adhere to its own brand, independent research and development model for self-development, to &quot;build a world-class national car brand&quot; for the industry target in the automotive industry into the world just a decade to become the new darling of the automotive industry: in 2008, BYD get &quot;stock god&quot; Buffett&#39;s favor; since 2010, BYD began a large-scale operation of new energy vehicles, has been promoted in 25 countries; 2014 Wang won the &quot;Zayed future Energy Prize&quot; Lifetime Achievement Award, BYD three green dream and re-electrification of urban public transport international recognition. This case concerned about the development strategy BYD automotive products, unique corporate culture and the company&#39;s three modules optimize the allocation of resources &quot;complementary&quot; to study the success of its innovation, aims to develop and adjust their business strategies in the development of innovative and developing effective business model to provide reference guide. This case applies to MBA teaching &quot;Technology innovation management&quot;, &quot;service innovation&quot; and other programs, especially in the case study discussed in terms of the use of technological innovations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新企业发展；企业文化；企业如何在中国市场环境中更好的发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-10</td>
                            </tr>
